<li id="cite_note-18"><b><a href="#cite_ref-18" title="">^</a></b> <a href="http://newsnet.byu.edu/story.cfm/57510" class="external text" title="http://newsnet.byu.edu/story.cfm/57510" rel="nofollow">BYU NewsNet - Snowboarder stereotype squelched</a></li>
<li id="cite_note-19"><b><a href="#cite_ref-19" title="">^</a></b> <a href="http://www.urbandictionary.com/define.php?term=steezy" class="external text" title="http://www.urbandictionary.com/define.php?term=steezy" rel="nofollow">Urban Dictionary: steezy</a></li>
</ol>
</div>
